<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00120</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT IMPLEMENTING THE PEOPLE’S RIGHT TO INFORMATION AND THE CONSTITUTIONAL POLICIES OF FULL PUBLIC DISCLOSURE AND HONESTY IN THE PUBLIC SERVICE AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : People’s Freedom Of Information Act</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Recognizes the right of the people to information on matters of public concern and adopts and implements a policy of full public disclosure of all its transactions involving the public interest, subject to the procedures and limitation provided by this Act.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>TAN, ANGELINA &quot;HELEN&quot; D.L. M.D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-06-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Reform</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON PUBLIC INFORMATION ON 2016-07-26</td></tr></table>